.TH GPT-SESSION 1 "2025-11-28" "SentinelShell"

.SH NAME
gpt-session - AI-augmented terminal session recorder for pentesters

.SH SYNOPSIS
gpt-session [command]

.SH DESCRIPTION
SentinelShell integrates OpenAI with Bash to record, summarize, redact, sync, and replay terminal sessions.

.SH COMMANDS
.TP
start
Start logging a session.

.TP
stop
Stop logging and generate an AI summary.

.TP
sync
Upload the session log to ChatGPT.

.TP
autosync-on N
Enable autosync every N minutes.

.TP
autosync-off
Disable autosync.

.TP
replay
Replay the last recorded session using scriptreplay.

.SH FILES
~/.gpt_sessions/

.SH AUTHOR
necr0bot
